  `judgments/chain-03.md` requires a promoted mechanism to reduce one named bad term or exclude one named bad transfer pattern in a quantitatively relevant portion of the full nonlinear burden.
  `attacks/chain-03.md` rejects any baseline phrased only as attractive cascade language.
- Obstruction:
