+# Provisional Step-011 Configuration Is Stretching Enstrophy Bottleneck Plus Dyadic Coupled Fluxes Plus A Role-Labeled Tao Screen
+
+Status: `INFERRED` provisional freeze with `VERIFIED` narrowing verdict
+
+The Step-011 local record does not support a full scope lock, but it does
+support one serious provisional configuration for the coupled energy-helicity
+chain.
+
+That narrowed configuration is:
+`stretching/enstrophy bottleneck` plus `dyadic coupled fluxes` plus an exact
+role-labeled helical packet audit with mandatory conjugate completion, frozen
+sign/amplitude/phase sheet data, and the five-part Tao canonicalization
+screen.
+
+Why this is the best-supported setup on disk:
+
+- `GOAL.md`, `CHAIN.md`, `winning-chain.md`, `judgments/chain-03.md`, and
+  `attacks/chain-03.md` repeatedly force Step 1 to name one bad term or bad
+  transfer pattern in stretching/enstrophy language rather than rely on a
+  generic continuation slogan;
+- `GOAL.md`, `CHAIN.md`, `selected/chain-03.md`, `winning-chain.md`, and
+  `planner.md` make `dyadic coupled fluxes` the strongest available first
+  package, even though the exact identity ledger for that package is still not
+  separately frozen on disk;
+- the existing factual packet-policy and Tao-screen notes already fix the
+  smallest honest support object and the right Tao-sensitive audit features for
+  exact-NS packet comparisons.
+
+So the honest Step-011 product is not an open menu. It is one provisional
+triple that later screening must either cash out or kill.
+
+Filed from:
